{"tid":1858443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[英國巴絲入] 大家有冇戴口罩返學","createTime":"2020-02-02T17:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T19:12:31.000Z","uid":345470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"41e11d711742769f61509660581431e72427bb39","tid":1858443,"uid":345470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"有冇人好似我咁on9 ，好想戴口罩但怕人地以為你係chinese 然後racist你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家 50 50緊聽日戴唔戴口罩返學/上堂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英國仲要係一個唔興戴口罩嘅地方來，我見到條街戴口罩嘅人真係0，連啲支那學生都唔戴 仆你個街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱啱係見到呢個post，我聽日會唔會上新聞俾人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人因戴口罩被英國人攻擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857801</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9654a1c0fbb2fd0573a15cfc9da7fdd422ef0dbf","tid":1858443,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"絲打？ <br />\n應該無事既帶都<br />\n不過巴打就難講"},{"pid":"57937da574b5623b3e76a13ee7a1c29dc09fd9c0","tid":1858443,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"帶一個係身 唔好戴"},{"pid":"8b93640a89a911ac196fe2e38c0524bdc3027a5c","tid":1858443,"uid":203799,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"外國真係無戴口罩習慣，戴口罩個啲通常都係好嚴重就死先戴<br />\n建議你上車先戴，一係放定幾個係袋，多人就戴"},{"pid":"28195e9e688fb41dbed2a609174b3e56eefca28b","tid":1858443,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"戴啦，買個FASHION D嘅扮FASHION ACCESSIORES。"},{"pid":"82c10ed424b4d916361771803e99f3e9d8c2e937","tid":1858443,"uid":346133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7QUrmPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QUrmPC.jpg&h=